item.title: Total
item.description: Hola Esta es una prueba library(dplyr) ## ## Attaching package: 'dplyr' ## The following objects are masked from 'package:stats': ## ## filter, lag ## The following objects are masked from 'package:base': ## ## intersect, setdiff, setequal, union library(ggplot2) mtcars <- mutate(mtcars,cyl=factor(cyl,ordered=TRUE,levels=c(4,6,8))) P <- ggplot(mtcars,aes(x=mpg)) + geom_histogram(binwidth=5) + labs(title = "Migración total en Mesoamérica", subtitle = "Aeee", caption = "Fuente: SEGOB 2011. \n \n obmime.com") P
